Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.38,0:00:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,边凝视着你边说下流的话\N波多野 结衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.79,0:00:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高贵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.59,0:00:17.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高贵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.80,0:00:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多人都说我看起来\N很高贵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.80,0:00:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是一般人眼中的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.27,0:00:32.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是实际上呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.42,0:00:48.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒...好棒...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.29,0:00:56.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒...肉棒...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.77,0:01:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋蛋...蛋蛋...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.45,0:01:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越是说这种下流的话.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.39,0:01:23.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的我，就会显露出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.20,0:01:31.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒...肉穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.80,0:01:35.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湿答答的肉穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.01,0:01:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一边装着很高雅的样子..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.09,0:01:58.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却又不停的说着下流的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.43,0:02:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒...我想舔肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.04,0:02:10.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想要大肉棒不停的插进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.71,0:02:18.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想要肉棒插进湿答答的肉穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.85,0:02:26.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想想舔肉棒..蛋蛋..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.86,0:02:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想舔肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.21,0:02:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒..被人这样看着..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.09,0:02:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办...好丢脸哦..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.56,0:03:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.16,0:03:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心跳越来越快了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.57,0:03:17.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里...还有这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.18,0:03:22.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都被人看着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.91,0:03:29.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该不会是想自慰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.45,0:03:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我是这样想的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.12,0:03:35.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想让人看哦..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.86,0:03:42.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.33,0:03:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我竟然想这种下流的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.01,0:03:53.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好丢脸哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.41,0:03:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.75,0:04:01.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是好让人同奋哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.17,0:04:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胸部..胸部被人看着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.70,0:04:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好丢脸哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.78,0:04:27.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是又好兴奋哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.18,0:04:38.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样摸着胸部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.59,0:04:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行..不行啦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.73,0:04:52.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.07,0:04:55.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.88,0:05:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.22,0:05:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样用力揉胸部..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.36,0:05:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么丢脸的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.37,0:05:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家做不到啦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.04,0:05:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是好舒服哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.45,0:05:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行...那里是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.99,0:05:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有那里不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.34,0:06:03.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行...好丢脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.41,0:06:06.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你看这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.41,0:06:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被你这样看着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.82,0:06:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好丢脸哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.55,0:06:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然好丢脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.16,0:06:21.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是又好兴奋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.76,0:06:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里..不行...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.17,0:06:33.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要摸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.92,0:06:56.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里被摸的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.20,0:07:08.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里....小豆子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.74,0:07:14.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你捏住它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.75,0:07:20.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里.....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.89,0:07:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里不行...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.36,0:07:29.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小豆子..好舒服.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.78,0:07:50.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行...好丢脸哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.79,0:07:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你看着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.86,0:08:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被这样盯着看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.66,0:08:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家...好丢脸哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.20,0:08:16.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是又好兴奋哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.03,0:08:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连后面也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.91,0:08:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请看我韵屁股
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.32,0:09:06.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家没让人看过屁股
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.93,0:09:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行...这样被人看着...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.93,0:09:16.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好兴奋哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.89,0:09:40.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再多打几下嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.24,0:10:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉穴..肉穴...好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.92,0:10:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手停不下来，
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.85,0:10:14.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行...这么下流的事..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.53,0:10:19.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家...会湿掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.53,0:10:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.88,0:10:36.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉穴好像被看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.02,0:10:45.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样掰开来的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.02,0:10:49.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉穴全被看光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.04,0:11:02.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行...这么近...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.64,0:11:05.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉穴的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.11,0:11:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很臭吧...好丢脸哦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.20,0:11:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家摸肉穴的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.54,0:11:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要仔细看哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.41,0:11:44.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手指...手指...插进来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.35,0:11:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.89,0:11:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事被人看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.42,0:11:56.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好丢脸哦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.09,0:11:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是又好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.50,0:12:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉穴好湿哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.17,0:12:15.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又、又一根插进来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.05,0:12:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.52,0:12:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么多手指插进来....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.60,0:12:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.67,0:12:40.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好丢脸哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.94,0:12:48.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.61,0:12:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么激烈...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.69,0:12:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好丢脸哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.95,0:13:01.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉穴...肉穴要高朝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.05,0:13:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好丢脸哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.06,0:13:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被看到高朝的样子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.80,0:13:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好丢脸哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.67,0:13:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温答答的肉穴也全部\N被看光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.34,0:13:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是人家好兴奋哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.55,0:14:03.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小豆子也变的这么硬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.02,0:14:10.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事竟然被人看到...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.77,0:14:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手指又插进来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.04,0:14:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全被人看光了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.58,0:14:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.45,0:14:35.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两根插进来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.33,0:14:47.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湿答答的肉穴好舒服哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.54,0:14:57.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乳头这样被拉住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.74,0:15:04.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家又要高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.15,0:15:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又要高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.91,0:15:35.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉穴动的好厉害...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.86,0:15:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里竟然有肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.07,0:16:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想要...好想要舔它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.62,0:16:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明就有人在旁边看..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.55,0:16:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是..可是好想舔哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.09,0:16:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.64,0:16:38.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舔了..人家舔了肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.59,0:16:52.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美味.. .太美味了....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.40,0:17:04.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒...碰到乳头了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.09,0:17:30.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嫱舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.36,0:17:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么激烈的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.47,0:18:14.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.14,0:18:21.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒摩擦的好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.81,0:18:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服...碰到小豆子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.11,0:18:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你从后面看嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.92,0:19:12.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插进来了...肉棒插进来了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.07,0:19:27.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.28,0:19:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插进来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.43,0:19:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再多看几下嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.37,0:19:56.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒插进来的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.17,0:20:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被人看着....好丢脸哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.18,0:20:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是好舒服哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.79,0:20:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚、脚在发抖..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.73,0:20:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么激烈的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.60,0:20:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家要高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.96,0:20:55.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被人看到高潮的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.90,0:20:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好丢脸哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.18,0:21:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你在多看一点嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.46,0:21:20.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒插进来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.26,0:21:26.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒插进我的肉穴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.93,0:21:30.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.14,0:21:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家要疯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.54,0:21:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明、明明就觉得好丢脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.02,0:21:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是又好兴奋哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.62,0:21:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再多看几下嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.36,0:22:00.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你看着人家高潮的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.64,0:22:12.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.42,0:22:59.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒...好舒服哦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.37,0:23:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美味哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.30,0:23:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒上都是肉穴的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.65,0:23:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有自己的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.99,0:23:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.14,0:23:48.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的手很美吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.94,0:23:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是有特剔保养过哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.81,0:24:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我每天都用这些手指头，
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.22,0:24:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自慰哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.30,0:24:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所我的这些手指:
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:25.44,0:24:27.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用这些手指...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:28.38,0:24:30.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抚摸你的肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:32.25,0:24:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想摸啊....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:38.92,0:24:40.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:41.32,0:24:45.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摸的到你的乳头哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.40,0:24:54.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变的很硬哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:01.75,0:25:04.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看看你的乳头
